TITLE: Adding Interceptors to Axios Instance (JavaScript)
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to add request interceptors to a custom Axios instance.  This allows you to apply specific interceptors to certain requests only. Dependencies: axios
SOURCE: https://github.com/sumsubstance/apptokenusageexamples/blob/master/JS/node_modules/axios/README.md#_snippet_21

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const instance = axios.create();
instance.interceptors.request.use(function () {/*...*/});
```

