TITLE: Axios Promise Usage
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates the recommended way to handle responses and errors using `axios.then` and `axios.catch`, replacing the deprecated `axios.success` and `axios.error` methods. This is the standard way to use promises with Axios.
SOURCE: https://github.com/sumsubstance/apptokenusageexamples/blob/master/JS/node_modules/axios/UPGRADE_GUIDE.md#_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
axios.get('some/url')
  .then(function (res) {
    /* ... */
  })
  .catch(function (err) {
    /* ... */
  });
```

